Package: icbs
Title: IBCS-Compliant Business Visualizations for ggplot2
Version: 3.0.10
Authors@R:
    person("Alejandro", "Hagan", , "alejandro.hagan@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create business visualizations following International Business
    Communication Standards (IBCS). Provides themes, color scales, variance
    charts, waterfall charts, scenario notation, and multi-panel layouts with
    connectors. Integrates with the marquee package for colored text labels.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
